{"tid":2241560,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"百鳩幾年前日本人已經極重視司法獨立","createTime":"2020-10-13T11:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T06:15:40.000Z","uid":54359,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1abe5dae5749dc1f781fbfc66d5a6d2dd1e6c9","tid":2241560,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"大津事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/大津事件\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E5%A4%A7%E6%B4%A5%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbS8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=63c31699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/大津事件</a><br />\n<br />\n日本刑法第116條大逆罪原先僅適用於傷者為日本皇室成員，外國的皇族在日本刑法中與一般人地位相同。如此一來，若傷害一般人即判處死刑，在法律層面上是說不過去的。當時的日本政府有意把刑法116條的適用對象「延伸」至外國皇族，以迎合俄國。此謀造成與絕對遵守法律的司法單位激烈的對立。<br />\n<br />\n當時的大審院院長兒島惟謙主張罪刑法定主義，認為「法治國家必須完全遵守法律」，以「刑法116條並非規定外國皇族」為由，消弭來自政府的壓力；並依據刑法第292條的規定（對一般人謀殺未遂罪），判決津田三藏無期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n反觀今時今日既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227ffb48c23edca24fadb76b9982202b21beb2af","tid":2241560,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:35:28.000Z","msg":"條友都係死咗"},{"pid":"394ab056d50c6b7b34e77659c812e2df8b01892d","tid":2241560,"uid":98473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"再再再反觀宜家日本司法制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfbe4cae465888f0f2737f1fb6d779d3e3589e2","tid":2241560,"uid":331739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"394ab056d50c6b7b34e77659c812e2df8b01892d","tid":2241560,"uid":98473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"再再再反觀宜家日本司法制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T11:46:46.0